Installation & Usage:
---------------------

Please visit the the OPIUM project web site at
http://opium.sourceforge.net for information on installation and
usage.

To compile OPIUM:

./configure
make

should work fine.  If there are problems, please see the files in
docs/ or look at the FAQ on the OPIUM homepage.  If all else fails,
please feel free to email the mailing list:

opium-talk@lists.sourceforge.net

to ask your question.

